taskInfo.hql: SELECT      0                            AS TRD_DATE    ,       T.BRANCH                      AS DEPT_ID     ,       T.CUST_CODE                   AS CUST_ID     ,       T.ACCOUNT                     AS CPTL_ACC_ID ,       T.SECU_ACC                    AS SCR_ACC_ID  ,       T2.MDL_DICTEN_CD              AS MKT_CD      ,      T1.SECU_CODE                  AS SCR_CD      ,       ''                            AS CAPT_TYPE_CD,       ''                            AS ROUG_TYPE_CD,       T.SHARE_OTD-T.SHARE_OTD_AVL   AS ROUG_QTY      FROM ODS.KGOB_SHARES T LEFT JOIN ODS.KGOB_SECURITIES T1 ON T.SECU_INTL=T1.SECU_INTL LEFT JOIN TEMP_DICT_CODE T2 ON CONCAT(TRIM(T.MARKET),TRIM(T.BOARD)) = T2.SSYS_DICTEN_CD AND T2.SYS_SRC ='KGOB' AND T2.MDL_DICT_CD ='DIMLS111'
